Package: shinyClaudeCodeUI
Title: Chat UI for Claude Code in Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kaiping", "Yang", email = "kaiping.yang@beigene.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Embed Claude Code as a chat-style UI inside Shiny applications using
    shinychat. Communicates with the Claude Code CLI via bidirectional stream-json
    protocol over processx pipes. Renders assistant responses as Markdown bubbles,
    tool calls as collapsible cards, and supports permission approval dialogs.
    Works behind corporate proxies like Posit Workbench and Posit Connect by
    routing all communication through Shiny's own WebSocket connection.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
